Package gov.nasa.pds.harvest.cfg

Class HarvestConfigurationType

java.lang.Object
gov.nasa.pds.harvest.cfg.HarvestConfigurationType
Direct Known Subclasses:
Harvest
public class HarvestConfigurationType extends Object
These are the basic options for the harvest configuration file. autogenFields: should not be used except in development testing load: tells where and how to harvest PDS4 labels fileInfo: option allowing filename prefixes to be replaced nodeName: the PDS node that this harvest run applies to productFilter: should not be used except in development testing registry: define the server harvest should use xpathMaps: allow constraints in the PDS4 label to control harvesting

Java class for harvest_configuration_type complex type.
